genresAdvancedInfo.name: tongan pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Tongan pop is a popular music genre from the Polynesian country of Tonga. The music is heavily influenced by traditional Tongan music and features a mix of modern and traditional instruments. The lyrics often focus on love and relationships, and the music is known for its catchy melodies and upbeat rhythms. Tongan pop has gained popularity in the Pacific Islands and among Tongan communities around the world.
